This programe is desighned to search for a specific word in multible files 
 ** the number of files N must be between 1 and 20
 ** max line length 80 character
 ** file name max 127 character

this programe is build on multi processes 
 ** the mainn pprocess create N child proceses
 ** each child process open one file and get the output
 ** output from child process send to the main process by temp files
 ** finally , after all children processes terminated , the main rea temp files and get the results

good luck
